This code is awfull but demonstrates what we want to achieve with this workshop in a crude but simple way. 
We use two components PHPTracker (http://php-tracker.org/) and LightOpenID (http://gitorious.org/lightopenid).
The PHPTracker's licence is available in the /lib/PHPTracker 
LightOpenId use the MIT license

The rest of the code is licensed under WTFPL (http://sam.zoy.org/wtfpl/) 

